ContentDesc_Arkadion - Halbschwergewicht: Having bested Black Cat, you prepare to face your second opponent─Honey B. Lovely. With the pheromones of a queen bee and the charm of a songstress, she enthralls her foes before finishing them with deadly venom. If you are to resist her charms, you must steel yourself for a captivating confrontation...
Instancecontenttextdata_39100_Text: The Honey B. Lovely show has begun!
Instancecontenttextdata_39101_Text: Here comes her fearsome venom strike!
Instancecontenttextdata_39102_Text: Now to savor the sweet sting of Honey B.'s charms.
Instancecontenttextdata_39103_Text: Oh, she's definitely feeling your love!
Instancecontenttextdata_39104_Text: Can the challenger resist the irresistible!? I know I can't.
Instancecontenttextdata_39105_Text: Alas, her charms were not to be denied!
Instancecontenttextdata_39106_Text: What's this? Honey B. has changed her routine!
Instancecontenttextdata_39107_Text: What a clash! Neither side is willing to yield!
Instancecontenttextdata_39108_Text: Let's put on a lovely show for the audience, hmm?
Instancecontenttextdata_39109_Text: A little taste to make it interesting.
Instancecontenttextdata_39115_Text: No hard feelings if I kill you?
Instancecontenttextdata_39116_Text: Oooh, what a delightful battle this is!
Instancecontenttextdata_39117_Text: Hope you're ready for me to steal your heart!
Instancecontenttextdata_39120_Text: Is everyone having a good time?
Instancecontenttextdata_39121_Text: What? Oh, you're kidding me, it didn't work?
Instancecontenttextdata_39122_Text: Your support means the world to me, everyone!
Instancecontenttextdata_39124_Text: B is for beat you to a bloody pulp!
Instancecontenttextdata_40700_Text: A vicious blow! That'll leave a mark!
Instancecontenttextdata_40701_Text: Even I felt that one! But the challenger's still standing!
Instancecontenttextdata_40704_Text: Oh my! The challenger went down hard!
Instancecontenttextdata_40705_Text: And they're down! Is it over already!?
Instancecontenttextdata_40706_Text: They're back on their feet! What grit!
Instancecontenttextdata_40707_Text: They're still in it! But for how long!?
Instancecontenttextdata_40708_Text: What power! Looks like someone isn't holding back!
